snippet.title: God of Rock - Announcement Trailer - Future Games Show Gamescom 2022
snippet.description: God of Rock is a rhythm fighting game from Modus Studios Brazil, starring divine duellists of musical fate. God of Rock is coming this winter to PC, PlayStation, Xbox and PC.
